snippet.title: KISS - Story Trailer
snippet.description: KISS is a love letter to the exciting world of K-pop! In this Life Simulator,you're the mighty manager who scouts for talent, manages their schedule, makes their budget, plans their social media, picks their music & their fashion! Debut the next hit K-pop idol group!
